comments.body:
> We want to get @ygalblum PR in first and then base this one off of it.

Do we?  I thought we gravitated more toward enforcing replicas to 1 and emit a warning because of all the limitations we face when running Podman on a single node in contrast to an orchestrated environment such as K8s.

@dcermak, how are you using replicas with Podman?  Would limiting replicas to 1 break some of your use cases?
